------------------------------------------------------------
-- Open Questions
------------------------------------------------------------

open_question "Should AgentSession be split into sub-specs (session-management.allium, extension-system.allium, compaction.allium) once the Clojure implementation begins?"

open_question "Extension event ordering: when multiple extensions handle the same event, is the order deterministic? Should the spec guarantee it?"

open_question "Compaction threshold: is config.auto_compaction_threshold a session-level or global setting? The code uses per-session settings but the config block implies global."

open_question "RPC mode: should the JSON stdio protocol be a separate allium spec, or is the surface declaration here sufficient?"

open_question "Skills collision policy: when two skills share the same name, the first discovered wins. Should this be configurable (warn / error / last-wins)?"
